-projective visualization(imagine that the bad things that happen to us happened instead to others.Helps to make us appreciate 
 the relative insignificance of the bad things that happen to us and will therefore prevent them from disrupting our tranquility)
-contemplating vs worrying.Learn to contemplate,not worry.
